@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oxjhai(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.79 + v2 + 0.68) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.98)) + ((v2 + 0.39 - v0 + 0.60) + 0.13))
    tmp = 0.03
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.81 + v0 + 0.58) - (v1 + 0.98 / v1 + 0.36)) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.99 / tmp + 0.10)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
